        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "God of our salvation, for the glory of thy Name.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The calamities suffered have not extinguished all faith or hope. God is still the God of Israel's salvation, ",
        "children": []
